    <item>
      <title>普京押注特朗普在为更多战争启动时向乌克兰提供</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/putin-bets-trump-delivers-on-ukraine-while-priming-for-more-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据莫斯科熟悉此事的人们说，俄罗斯仍在指望美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在乌克兰达成可接受的和平协议，尽管它准备继续战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/putin-bets-trump-delivers-on-ukraine-while-priming-for-more-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动了更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙的桑切斯宣布140亿欧元以减轻美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/spain-s-sanchez-launches-14-billion-plan-to-mitigate-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理佩德罗·桑切斯（Pedro Sanchez）表示，西班牙计划对美国对美国征收的关税进行141亿欧元（156亿美元）的援助和融资，同时还敦促欧盟为受影响的行业创建基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/spain-s-sanchez-launches-14-billion-plan-to-mitigate-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长亚当斯（Adams）将作为独立</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nyc-mayor-adams-to-seek-reelection-as-independent-politico-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）将作为独立的，放弃民主党初选的连任，因为他努力应对最近丢弃的联邦贿赂案的后果，这有助于降低他的认可等级，并使他的政治生存危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nyc-mayor-adams-to-seek-reelection-as-independent-politico-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥说，我们不会在北约退出更多地花费更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马可·鲁比奥（Marco Rubio）坚持认为，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府无意离开北约，即使美国特使要求军事联盟成员棘手支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非联盟teeters作为预算显示裂谷的扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-africa-s-coalition-teeters-as-budget-shows-widening-rift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的统治联盟有可能在其主要成员对拟议的税收增加的争议加深，使兰特的税收加剧之后，可能会破裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-africa-s-coalition-teeters-as-budget-shows-widening-rift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 06:18:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国想要我们谈话，准备减少贸易盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/thailand-pm-says-prepared-to-deal-with-us-tariffs-plans-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据总理佩顿顿·辛纳瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）称，泰国准备应对特朗普政府征收的36％互惠关税的后果，他表示该国准备采取措施在谈判后采取措施减少与美国的贸易盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/thailand-pm-says-prepared-to-deal-with-us-tariffs-plans-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收压力“朋友”莫迪以迅速达成贸易协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-piles-pressure-on-friend-modi-with-26-tariff-on-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对印度的关税率高于预期，这可能会促使总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）加速与美国的贸易会谈，以最大程度地减少对亚洲第三大经济体的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-piles-pressure-on-friend-modi-with-26-tariff-on-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:32:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税会在全球经济中引起冲击波</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在一个世纪内征收美国最陡峭的美国关税，他加强了重塑全球经济的竞选活动，引发了报复的威胁，并在全球市场上抛弃了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
